mass        1 28.0855

pair_style  sw
pair_coeff  * * Si.sw Si
Reading sw potential file Si.sw with DATE: 2007-06-11
neighbor    1.0 bin

# relax to the exact stress-free geometry: finite differences need it
fix         1 all box/relax iso 0.0 vmax 0.001
minimize    1.0e-12 1.0e-12 1000 10000
