# --- finite-difference dynamical matrix at the Gamma point ---
# eskm: mass-weighted output in 1/fs^2, so sqrt(eigenvalue)/(2 pi) is in THz.
dynamical_matrix all eskm 1.0e-6 file dynmat.dat binary no
